//assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bvma4wawq3fr-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bvma4wawq3fr-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bvma4wawq3fr-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> Kamitsubaki Studio的观众等待着现场演出，他也与Ciel -Chan合作。</p><p>铃铛的声音在场地响起，<strong>终于开始了！</strong> Kamitsubaki Studio Live从通常的宏伟电影开始！</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.dbhunz1jrg3l-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.dbhunz1jrg3l-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.dbhunz1jrg3l-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.dbhunz1jrg3l-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.dbhunz1jrg3l-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.dbhunz1jrg3l-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.dbhunz1jrg3l-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>在第一首歌<strong>“ Iku之城”</strong>的同时，灯光照亮了Ciel -chan站在舞台上。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.mxee90f0zegx-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.mxee90f0zegx-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.mxee90f0zegx-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.mxee90f0zegx-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.mxee90f0zegx-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.mxee90f0zegx-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.mxee90f0zegx-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 1.64em;">哇，这是一个现场！ ！活着沉浸式的感觉！ ！</span></strong></p><p>根据up -tempo的歌曲，灯光又一次切换，花朵的发光效果会颤动，ciel -chan会对表演感到兴奋，说：“让我们今天一起兴奋！”</p><p>毕竟，总是在屏幕和屏幕上的Ciel -Chan<strong>在我面前在我面前！</strong>这是虚拟歌手VR Live独​​有的兴奋。您还可以在舞台上的大型监视器上看到Ciel -chan的微妙表达。</p><p>在户外空间（例如废墟）中使用照明的现场表演是一种空间生产​​，实际上不容易完成。这是虚拟的最喜欢的部分，您可以在充分表达艺术家对艺术家的看法的空间中享受现场表演。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ipkylzuqdnhz-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ipkylzuqdnhz-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ipkylzuqdnhz-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ipkylzuqdnhz-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ipkylzuqdnhz-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ipkylzuqdnhz-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ipkylzuqdnhz-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.f1wq44119gxi-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024