561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.qqp0bit7zt1c-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>在最后的生锈中<strong>，舞台将壮观的日落飞过另一侧</strong>，但是正如歌词所暗示的那样，能够去任何地方真是太好了！ 您可以简单地享受高质量的VR体验。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ykhytxxk6q9b-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ykhytxxk6q9b-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ykhytxxk6q9b-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ykhytxxk6q9b-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ykhytxxk6q9b-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ykhytxxk6q9b-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ykhytxxk6q9b-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7y8zreqm1zyl-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7y8zreqm1zyl-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7y8zreqm1zyl-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7y8zreqm1zyl-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7y8zreqm1zyl-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7y8zreqm1zyl-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7y8zreqm1zyl-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>顺便说一句，在展示现场表演的第一首歌和第二首歌已经结束，从这里开始，这是将在现场直播的第一部分。</p><p> <strong>“我将引导您进入您内心的世界。”</strong></p><p>嗯〜在哪里？ ？ 突然，前部变成白色...</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2mu6w1s0fkau-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2mu6w1s0fkau-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2mu6w1s0fkau-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2mu6w1s0fkau-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2mu6w1s0fkau-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2mu6w1s0fkau-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2mu6w1s0fkau-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 1.64em;">我在一个我不知道的空间中。</span></strong></p><p><strong>这在哪里……？ ？ ？</strong></p><p>此外，去过那里的许多观众已经走了，<strong>它已被转移到一个只有大约10个人的小空间中。</strong> （我稍后知道，每个空间的人数似乎都不同，而我恰好是一个很小的空间。）</p><p>第三首歌<strong>“ Buri Talk”</strong>突然诗歌融入了困惑和四处走动的观众的耳朵。 Kamitsubaki Studio这是歌手理由歌曲的封面。</p><p>像石头制成的祭坛这样的舞台，就像鸟篮在黑暗的天空中。西尔 -  chan周围被大花所包围。</p><p><strong>关闭！</strong> <strong>Ciel -chan感觉非常接近</strong>，可能是因为与观众几乎没有高度差异。<br />就像我拜访了Ciel的心一样。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.326dvuq32qc7-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.326dvuq32qc7-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/