 ！这是“幻想戏剧” ...！</strong></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>即使在VR Live中，您可以自由地设计一个空间，也是准备像舞台一样作为表演体验的舞台。<br />另一方面，我觉得没有太多的生产破坏了到目前为止的整个空间，并将<strong>其扔进了代表歌曲世界视图的空间</strong>。使用舞台和观众座位作为舞台设备之一的生产是使用VR的沉浸式感觉的作品。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-26-34.694_1920x1080.png"><img data-dominant-color="38426c" data-has-transparency="false" style="--dominant-color: #38426c;" decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="not-transparent alignnone size-full wp-image-252446" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-26-34.694_1920x1080.png" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-26-34.694_1920x1080.png 1920w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-26-34.694_1920x1080-300x169.png 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-26-34.694_1920x1080-1024x576.png 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-26-34.694_1920x1080-768x432.png 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-26-34.694_1920x1080-1536x864.png 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-22-21.726_1920x1080.png"><img data-dominant-color="444649" data-has-transparency="false" style="--dominant-color: #444649;" decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="not-transparent alignnone size-full wp-image-252447" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-22-21.726_1920x1080.png" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-22-21.726_1920x1080.png 1920w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-22-21.726_1920x1080-300x169.png 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-22-21.726_1920x1080-1024x576.png 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-22-21.726_1920x1080-768x432.png 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-22-21.726_1920x1080-153